videos.description: Standford took down the number 9 ranked Washington Huskies on a Friday night match up as Bryce Love ran for 166 yards and three touchdowns. Stanford had 20 unanswered points in the second half that led them to their upset victory.
videos.title: College Football: Stanford upsets Washington

videos.description: Ohio State had the largest win over Michigan State in series history winning 48-3. Mike Weber had a career game with 162 rushing yards and 2 touchdowns for the Buckeyes.
videos.title: College Football: Ohio State takes down Michigan State

videos.description: LSU takes home the Golden Boot for the second year in a row beating Arkansas 33-10. Derrius Guice was all over the field for the Tigers with 147 rushing yards and 3 touchdowns.
videos.title: College Football: LSU slides past Arkansas
